{
  "stem": "21648.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they start to beat him up, and they want to kill him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I grab my hand I have now, and the bullet went through my right here, my [? palm. ?] And I stopped the-- the bullet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here somehow he survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't kill him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I was working in the-- where the soldiers are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in the morning, we used to go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they undresed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They showered us with cold water, and we got dressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to the barracks, they call the barracks, to clean the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was our doing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to leave my baby with other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With other people, with neighbors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter, my husband, and I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your house-- my house was demolished when the war, when they was fighting already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German was going out and the Russian was coming in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was hiding everywhere we could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it was dead people on the street, we rolled onto the dead people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was some [? bushes ?] [? between-- ?] it's unbearable to tell and to explain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I can't explain those things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was already Russian bombs and German bombs together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They was fighting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They was going back, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or the Russian was coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was survived by the Russian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how long were you in the ghetto for?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I was in the ghetto a little more than a year, and then I ran away from the ghetto to a [? small. ?] Why did we run away to the-- from the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the ghetto working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was giving up numbers for the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
